      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPICE ALLEY (7) returns without a trial but showed enough in her debut campaign to suggest she had some talent. Budler and Potter are teaming up strongly of late and the barrier should see her get every chance. Looks set for a bold effort on resumption. BAREFOOTINTHESNOW (4) trialled well on this surface a couple of weeks ago and draws the inside for JVO which is a strong push for her chances. Finds the right race today and it wouldn't surprise to see her get the job done. THE ULTIMATE STAR (3) comes through the same trial as BAREFOOTINTHESNOW and was strong late in the trial there. Can sit just off the speed in the run and launch a strong attack late in the race. MONTE BRAVEHEART (2) is here off a long break and while he may not be a winning proposition here, he's worth following so we can make some money off him in his future runs.",
